title: MST3K Neato Labels
description:
DVD labels for the 35 DVD set of MST3K episodes that is currently in the process of being uploaded. These were created using the MediaFace 5 software that is included with the Neato labeling system.

I am not the person who is uploading the 35 DVDs, just a fan how created these labels for his own use and thought others might like them as well. And yes, I know DVDs 34 and 35 are ugly-there&#039;s just a ton of info, you could easily open them up and make them look a bit neater if you didn&#039;t want the listing on the disk.
